    "4006523": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "And this flowerpot was passed down to me as a family treasure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "It's certainly no coincidence that it appeared here and became the entrance to the mirage. It's almost as if... it's giving me a chance to make up for past regrets."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Regrets about what?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "There was once a time when the Kaedeharas were an illustrious clan in Inazuma."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "After the Raiden Gokaden incident, our clan's fortunes took a turn for the worse. By the time of my generation, our downfall was complete."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Later, I fled Inazuma as I didn't want be arrested. With no one left in the Kaedehara Clan, the authorities confiscated everything in our home, including this bonsai."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Like my ancestors before me, I think I'd like to try it out for myself... recreate a favorite scene from my travels and place it into this pot."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "... *sigh*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Since the contents of this bonsai affect the mirage, I'd at least like to try my hand at making something."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "But what style? Should I use plants for the bonsai like my great-grandfather, or rocks like my father and grandfather..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "...Perhaps a rock garden would suit me better."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So do you need any supplies to make this bonsai?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "I think I'll need a set of tools and some rocks that can be carved and made into decorations."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Got it, we'll help you look!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "We might just get lucky. If the pot's here, then surely other stuff related to crafting bonsai can't be far away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "I concur! Lord Kazuha, take heart in your search, for my retinue and I shall help you retrieve your missing treasures."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Thank you, everyone."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "4006515": {
        "Desc": "Discuss with everyone",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "So the bonsai pot belonged to your ancestors? Seems a shame to leave it empty like this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "Hmm, Kazuha, what do you think about maybe putting a little something inside it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Alright."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Though I still don't understand why it has appeared here, I can give that a try."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eek!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
