    "4006606": {
        "Desc": "Follow the path",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kageharu",
                    "T": "...This will do. Ah, Kazuha, you've come just at the right moment. What do you think of this rock carving?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "It's very intricate."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kageharu",
                    "T": "I based it on a mountain scene I saw in a book. You know, there are nations in this world where the mountains reach all the way up into the clouds. If only I had the chance to see them with my own eyes..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Father, you can go anywhere whenever you want."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kageharu",
                    "T": "That's not true. Though the Kaedehara Clan is far from what it used to be, I still bear all the same responsibilities as the clan heads before me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kageharu",
                    "T": "But then again... continuing in the way of our forefathers, sacrificing everything for our declining clan... is it really worth it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "But I... I don't understand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kageharu",
                    "T": "...Kazuha, there's one thing I want you to always remember."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kageharu",
                    "T": "Family ties are important, but you ought to not let them hold you back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kageharu",
                    "T": "Family only exists because of the people in it. If we are unhappy, how can we hope to build a joyful one?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kageharu",
                    "T": "The events of the past have had a profound impact on our family, but they are not your burden to carry."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kageharu",
                    "T": "...If you ever grow tired of this tedious life, just drop everything and go off on a journey, see the world. Remember, Kazuha, don't let yourself get tied down in life."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Yes, father."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
