    "4006617": {
        "Desc": "Look for Kazuha",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Thought we might find you trapped here again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Haha, yeah, it seems those are the rules."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We entered that maze in the mirage again, but the scene was different this time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You tell Kazuha what you saw..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "The mood was more deflated, and the place more humbly furnished... yes, that makes sense."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "What you saw was the Kaedehara Clan in decline."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We saw you in the mirage too, but you looked a little different than now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Indeed, I most certainly agree."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "Compared to the Lord Kazuha before us now, the mirage we saw appeared lost, with the burden of fate weighing heavily upon him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "I can confirm that. His fate was a heavy burden indeed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "That means I am older and wiser now. I am sorry you had to see my less mature former self."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "For a long time after leaving Inazuma, I've lived the life of a drifter. But this is no bad thing, because I learned much from the experience."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "I wish that I could've met my past self, too. If he saw me, I know that he would understand:"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Life is a long journey, and that's why I must travel far and wide."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
